snippet.title: Heretic Hunt CE3 2016 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer that was first shown at ce3 2016.
Take a look a the work in progress know as Heretic Hunt.
This single player mod will take you though various locations both similar and brand new with weapons from many halo games along with custom ones never before seen. Join in on this halo 2 based even on both the heretic and the covenant side. This mod is not quiet done and has a lot to go before it is. Keep updated with this youtube channel.
